    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >MANAGE YOUR OWN MUSIC STUDIO!</h2><br>Congratulations! You're about to buy your own music studio! <br>To strive in the music industry you must:<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Scout and Hire Bands</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Train your musicians</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Schedule gigs and albums</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Deal with the musicians personal problems</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Manage your money and reputation</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1792520/extras/9b9d961971126558906bc0f2319bd900.poster.avif?t=1641567365\" width=616 height=236 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1792520/extras/9b9d961971126558906bc0f2319bd900.webm?t=1641567365\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1792520/extras/9b9d961971126558906bc0f2319bd900.mp4?t=1641567365\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >ROCK STAR MANAGER FEATURES</h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Scouting and potential system</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Randomly generated bands and musicians</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>News feed that will keep track of your actions</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Trait System for the band's frontman</li></ul><br>Good luck in your journey. I'll surely root for you!",
